\par\par \b \uc2  Rationale of additional  \highlight22\uc2 tax \highlight\uc2  reform. \b0\par\par\uc2 1,044 \uc2 words\par \uc2 21 April 2003\par \uc2 The Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par  7 \par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2003 The Jakarta Post\par \par \uc2  Sofjan Wanandi, Chairman, Committee for National \b \highlight22\uc2 Economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  Recovery (KPEN), Jakarta \par \par \uc2  The government has often boasted of its success in achieving \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenue targets as set in its state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 . This claim is correct if the refund that has yet to be resolved is overlooked. But given the current \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  system, a question arises as to whether the performance of \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  administration in term of the revenue does give a true picture of the situation. In other words, whether the revenue has represented a net figure rather than a gross figure. \par \par \uc2  The question is related to refunds that have not been realized, including those based on the rulings by the \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  court. If this is taken into account the \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenue will likely be much less than what the government likes to claim. \par \par \uc2  This condition is certainly not conducive to investment, which has already been stifled by the \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  caused by the war in Iraq and other external and internal factors. \par \par \uc2  What is then the most appropriate approach to achieve the two goals at the same time, i.e. to enhance \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenue without impeding investment. \par \par \uc2  The best approach is to embark on another \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  reform, legally and administratively. Ideally, \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  reform aims at eliminating defects in the current laws, or adjusting the \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  best suited to current development. Based on current laws and their implementing regulations, \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  reform should cover two main areas, namely the law on \b \highlight22\uc2 taxation\b0 \highlight\uc2  procedure and the income \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  law and the value added \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  law. \par \par \uc2  The amendments of \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  laws initiated in 2000 put too much emphasis on revenue while other factors that may contribute to \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenue in the long run have been overlooked. The law on \b \highlight22\uc2 taxation\b0 \highlight\uc2  procedure addresses the issue as to how \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  compliance is carried out by taxpayers on one side, and how the enforcement is conducted by \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  administration on the other side. \par \par \uc2  Ideally, the law on procedure that is supposed to prescribe the procedures for \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  compliance and its enforcement should clearly stipulate that taxpayers' rights and obligations. It should also guarantee that the enforcement by \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  administration does not go beyond what has been stipulated in the law. \par \par \uc2  But the current practice does not indicate the proper philosophy of the procedure. And most crucial is that in complying with the \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  law taxpayer and \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  administration should be on equality in term of their obligations to the laws. In other words, should a taxpayer not comply with the law it must be penalized in accordance with the law. And the same principle should also apply to \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  officials who implement the law in breach of the provisions contained therein. \par \par \uc2  Thus, the recommendations on issues governed by law on procedure are focused on two main issues: First, provisions that stipulate \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  audit, and second is to protect taxpayers' rights, especially in the areas of refunds and objections. \par \par \uc2  Income \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  and value added \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  reform should serve two main goals - to enhance \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenue and to establish a favorable investment climate. The two objectives seem to be contradictory but actually they are not. \par \par \uc2  The revenue enhancement should be directed to transactions that have not been properly addressed in the law, while a favorable investment climate does not necessarily mean granting \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  incentives. A conducive investment climate can be achieved through the adoption of "\b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  neutral principle" and establishing legal certainty. \par \par \uc2  Again, the \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  amendment initiated in 2000 did not address issues that encourage investment. \par \par \uc2  In general terms, the law on \b \highlight22\uc2 taxation\b0 \highlight\uc2  procedure provides taxpayers' rights and obligations. But under the current provisions, some of them do not reflect the quality of position between taxpayers and \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  officers in front of the \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  laws. And this is clearly evident in the area of \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  audit and refund. \par \par \uc2  Under the self-assessment system the role of \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  audit is to ensure that taxpayers abide by the law. It is carried out to ensure that taxpayers fully disclose their income but this is possible only if certain conditions are met. \par \par \uc2  The caveat, though, is that the current law also provides that the purpose of audit is to make sure that taxpayers comply with the law and for other purposes. \par \par \uc2  The effect of the broadening of the definition is that \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  audits can be conducted for broader purposes in addition to securing the self-assessment system. The effect is that the self-assessment system has become an official-assessment. \par \par \uc2  There are several approaches to address the issue: First, the \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  audit is conducted to ensure that taxpayers comply with the law under self-assessment system, and second, the audit is carried after examination is done. In such a case the definition extends to cover both the terms "\b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  audit" as well as "examination". \par \par \uc2  In addition, certain conditions should be met prior to the conduct of \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  audits. This issue is closely related to the "audit selection" criteria. Under the present practice, there are a number of criteria used to carry out audits, such as \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  returns that shows losses, claims for refund, liquidation etc. The criteria is so broad that practically nearly all taxpayers are liable to \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  audits. \par \par \uc2  One of the appropriate approaches is that \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  audits should be used as a tool to ensure that taxpayers have complied with the law. In other words, audit selection criteria is set within the framework of a self-assessment system. It will be conducted only if \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  administration has reliable data that has not been reported in the \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  return. Prior to the audit an examination should be carried out to ensure that the targeted taxpayer has not fully disclosed his income. \par \par \uc2  The law stipulates that as a result of an audit, an assessment notice will be issued where it requires an additional \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  payable plus penalty. However, the law does not explicitly prescribe the penalty applicable to \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  officials in case there is an abuse in the \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  audit process. The law merely refers to penalty stipulated in government regulations that governs the conduct of civil servants. This will not deter delinquent \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  auditors to abuse their power for their own interest. \par \par \uc2  KPEN is a forum of the private sector to advise the government on \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  issues. \par \par \uc2  Copyright 2003 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020030421dz4l00009\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
