r \uc2  Aside from the countertrade deals, the ministry also plans to boost promotional activities in nontraditional markets such as the Middle East, East European countries, Africa, Latin America and East Asia to help raise export earnings. \par \par \uc2  "In October, for example, we will hold an expo in the United Arab Emirates," Rini said. \par \par \uc2  Indonesia's major non-oil and gas exports are textiles, footwear, timber-based products and electronics. \par \par \uc2  Indonesia's non-oil and gas exports during the first quarter of this year increased by 9.4 percent to $11.17 billion, from $10.17 billion in the same period of 2001. \par \par \uc2  Currently, the country's exports to nontraditional markets account for about 8 percent of total exports. \par \par \uc2  Copyright 2003 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020030528dz5t0005w\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
