 Bali, the Iraq war and the outbreak of SARS, to mention a few, all proved to have further derailed the world's \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  recovery. \par \par \uc2  Tommaso said that, based on those challenges the world currently faces - in what he called extra \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainties\b0 \highlight\uc2  after Sept. 11 - the expectation of a pick up "is more subject to a negative than a positive risk." \par \par \uc2  "And finally it's also true that the exceptionally high growth rates of the 90s are unlikely to be repeated in the near future. \par \par \uc2  "But I think that the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  analysis that underlies the projection of a pick up is a solid analysis and should not be discarded too readily. I do hope it proves to be true," he added. \par \par \uc2  Copyright 2003 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020030714dz7c000bp\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
