lution," he said, adding that disputing parties can also save time and money when using the service of mediators.  \par \par \uc2 PMN is open to any party who wants to resolve a commercial dispute. It offers mediation services for a wide range of commercial disputes, including wage issues, debt restructuring and big business transactions.  \par \par \uc2 Members of PMN are professional mediators, most of whom have been working at the Jakarta Initiative Task Force (JITF), which has received praise for its success in mediating disputes between foreign creditors and the country's private sector.  \par \par \uc2 Established in 1998 upon the request of the International Monetary Fund (IMF), JITF was tasked to help restructure huge dollar-dominated debts owed by the private sector to their creditors, mostly outside of Indonesia.  \par \par \uc2 JITF has successfully helped restructure over US$20 billion in private debts.  \par \par \uc2 Copyright 2003 The Jakarta Post.   \par \par \uc2 Document JKPOST0020030904dz950000t\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
